      所有方法 实例方法 具体方法 
      限定符和类型 方法和说明
      <T> void add(int what, Request<T> request, OnResponseListener<T> responseListener)
      Add a request task to download queue, waiting for execution, if there is no task in the queue or the number of tasks is less than the number of thread pool, will be executed immediately.
      void cancelAll()
      Cancel all requests, Already in the execution of the request can't use this method
      void cancelBySign(Object sign)
      All requests for the sign specified in the queue, if you are executing, will interrupt the task
      void start()
      Start polling the request queue, a one of the implementation of the download task, if you have started to poll the download queue, then it will stop all the threads, to re create thread execution.
      void stop()
      Polling the queue will not be executed, and this will not be canceled.

    • 构造器详细资料

      • RequestQueue

        public RequestQueue(ImplRestParser implRestParser,
                    int threadPoolSize)
        Create request queue manager.
        参数:
        implRestParser - download the network task execution interface, where you need to implement the download tasks that have been implemented.
        threadPoolSize - number of thread pool.

    • 方法详细资料

      • start

        public void start()
        Start polling the request queue, a one of the implementation of the download task, if you have started to poll the download queue, then it will stop all the threads, to re create thread execution.

      • add

        public <T> void add(int what,
                    Request<T> request,
                    OnResponseListener<T> responseListener)
        Add a request task to download queue, waiting for execution, if there is no task in the queue or the number of tasks is less than the number of thread pool, will be executed immediately.
        类型参数:
        T - T
        参数:
        what - the "what" will be the response is returned to you, so you can introduce multiple Request results in an A with what, please distinguish which is the result of the Request.
        request - Request
        responseListener - OnResponseListener

      • stop

        public void stop()
        Polling the queue will not be executed, and this will not be canceled.

      • cancelBySign

        public void cancelBySign(Object sign)
        All requests for the sign specified in the queue, if you are executing, will interrupt the task
        参数:
        sign - this sign will be the same as sign's Request, and if it is the same, then cancel the task.

      • cancelAll

        public void cancelAll()
        Cancel all requests, Already in the execution of the request can't use this method
